        <hl1>Calling Broadway's Fondest Regards</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The word around the theater district lately is that the awarding of this season's Tonys on Sunday is more or less a fait accompli: This one's a lock, that category's pretty much wrapped up, this actor can't lose. Campbell Robertson makes some predictions, informed by a highly informal poll. Page 5.</p>
